In the event you are...divested of your property, we shall collect your furnishings for safekeeping─those which may be safely removed, that is. Furthermore, should the property in question be an estate, you may claim indemnification for four–fifths the plot's value.
However, pray understand that we offer these services only as a courtesy─and for a limited time.
There are no abandoned possessions to be claimed.
